sentences: In its conclusions (FCCC/SBI/2010/L.9), the SBI notes that the exchange of views by parties on this issue has, in conjunction with additional information provided by the Secretariat and the Office of Legal Affairs of the United Nations, further enhanced the understanding of the parties.

The SBI also notes the progress made in developing the draft treaty arrangements contained in the annex and agrees to continue its consideration of this issue at SBI 33 on the basis of the text contained in the annex, with a view to concluding these arrangements as soon as possible.
